body:
• Normally, Tony isn’t the jealous type
  • He’s super confident and has no reason to worry about other guys
  • Because he knows he’s better than them
  • He knows no one will ever love you as much as he does
  • Or buy you as many things as he does (because he spoils the shit out of you)
  • Or make love to you the way he does
  • He’s seen and watched many guys hit on you
  • Always with a smirk
  • Because he knows they’ll never have you
  • He’ll always cut in and call you “Darling” or “Baby” and kiss you in front of the guy
  • One thing he will not stand for is when someone puts their hands on you
  • He will go ballistic
  • You do not want to be within 10 feet of him when someone does that
  • Nor do you want to be the guy that does that to you
  • So there you are, one of Tony’s fancy parties
  • Wearing a tight blue sparkly dress with a cut out between your breasts, highlighting your cleavage perfectly
  • Tony actually bought the dress for you and told you to wear it tonight
  • You were standing out on the balcony, looking out at the sun that was starting to set
  • When a guy walked over and started chatting you up
  • You gave in a little bit, always giving them something to bite on because you know your man will swoop in any second with the drinks he just left to get
  • “That dress looks amazing on you”
  • “This old thing?”
  • But then it happened
  • He put his hand on your shoulder
  • You tense up
  • “Just imagine it on my bedroom floor” he said in your ear
  • His hand glides down your back
  • He was bolder than you’re used to
  • You raised your brows at him, wishing you had that drink now to chuck it in his face
  • His hand caresses your waist
  • You were about to push him away when you felt his hand tense up and leave your body
  • “What the hell do you think you’re doing”
  • You heard Tony’s voice from behind you
  • You turned around and saw him and knew
  • He was pissed
  • He was holding onto the guys wrist
  • “My bad, I didn’t know she was spoken for”
  • The guy said, you could see Tony’s wrist turning white by how hard he was holding his wrist
  • “Don’t you know, it’s never okay to touch a lady like that”
  • “I-I’m sorry, it won’t happen again” the guy pleaded, trying to grab onto Tony’s hand to get him to release his wrist
  • Tony wasn’t budging
  • “Let go of my arm, man!”
  • “Tony…”
  • You spoke up, knowing how pissed he was
  • You put your hand on his chest and grabbed his hand
  • “Next time, I’ll break it”
  • Tony threatened, releasing his wrist
  • The guy quickly walked away, looking mortified
  • “I should have broken his fucking wrist”
  • He said, clearly still pissed off
  • “Thank you for that, but I’m glad you didn’t. You could get in a lot of trouble for that”
  • You said, rubbing his shoulders
  • “I don’t care how much trouble I’d get in. He touches you again, I kill him”
  • You studied his face, knowing there was no calming him down from this or changing his mind
  • You just grabbed onto the back of his neck and kissed him
  • All you were thinking was: Damn, he’s pretty hot when he’s jealous
